# HARNESS governance

Follow `AGENT.md`, `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`, `docs/specs/SDD.md`, and the active task brief before editing. Keep access read-only by default, avoid secrets and production data, document open points, and update relevant docs/checklists/tests with every material change.
